      <title>印度大学入学考试丑闻蔓延 引发刑事调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/india-college-entrance-exam-scandal-spreads-with-criminal-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着学生对这一日益严重的丑闻的抗议日益增多，印度政府已对医学院校全国入学考试中的作弊和腐败指控展开刑事调查，并撤掉了负责处理考试的机构负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/india-college-entrance-exam-scandal-spreads-with-criminal-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 05:47:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
